parameters.name: CenId
parameters.description: The ID of the CEN instance to which the VPC is attached.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description:
The number of entries to return on each page. Valid values: 10 to 500.

Default value:

*   If you do not specify a value, the default value is 20.
*   If this parameter is set to a value greater than 500, the default value is 500.

parameters.name: NetworkInterfaceId
parameters.description: The ID of ENI N. Valid values of N: 1 to 100.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The pagination token that is used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results. You do not need to specify this parameter for the first request. You must specify the token that is obtained from the previous query as the value of NextToken.

parameters.name: PrimaryIpAddress
parameters.description: The primary private IPv4 address of the ENI.

parameters.name: VSwitchId
parameters.description: The ID of a vSwitch in the VPC. You can specify only one vSwitch in each call.
